{"tid":1345791,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[緊急] 宜家民意戰已經輸哂  !!!!","createTime":"2019-07-22T02:49:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T03:55:24.000Z","uid":28307,"like":66,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"db98e059e5bd5dc4febea396afe4cf293aa07d95","tid":1345791,"uid":28307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T02:49:35.000Z","msg":"係 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">香港港共軍政府 輸撚哂呀 !</span></span> 文宣組絕對唔可以放過呢個機會 !<br />\n<br />\n元朗呢單黑黑相衛 元朗內外警黑合作 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">警黑一家親</span> </strong></span>已經通哂街 ! <br />\n又比人踢爆左元朗警方 事前已經知曉並有心配合 元朗鄉黑 一齊打當日既示威者<br />\n<br />\n當日721 白衫仔公然在元朗全日舞刀弄棍 並在MTR中多次毆打 普通市民<br />\n事件中 全日並沒有任何執法單位介入 !<br />\n反而 刻意配合 白衫仔(元朗鄉黑) 毆打普通市民 <br />\n(E.G. 多次報警被CUT線 , 多間警局落閘 , 報警後沒有受理 , <br />\n事情中白衫仔多次在警方面前經過 , 警方與白衫仔談笑風生 ,<br />\n白衫仔全日舞刀弄棍 有流血事件,警方卻說看不到有人持攻擊性武器<br />\n等待白衫仔離開後 , 警方到場卻沒有執法 , 反而多次恐嚇普通市民 ...不能盡錄)<br />\n<br />\n所謂既執法單位不斷製造  <strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">白色恐怖</span> </strong>及 <strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">黑色恐怖</span></strong><br />\n但好可惜既係 市民並沒有因此而害怕 ! 反而 堅定左我地既立場 我地呢次抗爭既正當性<br />\n <br />\n多謝呢次事件大大幫左我地<br />\n1. <strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">堅定左我地既立場</span></span></strong><br />\n勇武既人會更勇武<br />\n中立/冷感既人看到更多不公義<br />\n藍絲 立場動搖<br />\n<br />\n2.  <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">勇武/和理非的 正當性</span></strong></span><br />\n警方對 手無寸鐵既示威者 訴以暴徙定性 以槍屠殺我地!<br />\n但對 全日舞刀弄棍 公然包庇 扮睇唔到 並事前配合 !<br />\n<br />\n多間警局落閘 ! 多次報警被CUT線 !  <br />\n香港已無維持治安既部隊  只有受中央任命並暴力對待人民既警察<br />\n人民的警察已完全失去 道德性 正當性 <br />\n香港政府已 陷入 軍政府狀態  !<br />\n<br />\n <strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">邊撚個死三毛 再講失敗論<br />\n 請屌柒佢 ''扑''柒佢 撚有失敗過</span> </span> </strong>"},{"pid":"cdc547df4a6df1a91c4ce7f31c2760813535090d","tid":1345791,"uid":28307,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T02:50:58.000Z","msg":"認同的 請幫推 !<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efbf26c8d56dc8d8198376cfe835062391ffcc75","tid":1345791,"uid":147949,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T02:52:37.000Z","msg":"［正視聽］究竟仲理民意做乜<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1344270\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1344270</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d920063ff9ebb975e5848670ae34bc01e1f38a1e","tid":1345791,"uid":147949,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"efbf26c8d56dc8d8198376cfe835062391ffcc75","tid":1345791,"uid":147949,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T02:52:37.000Z","msg":"［正視聽］究竟仲理民意做乜<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1344270\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1344270</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T02:53:03.000Z","msg":"理性探討民意"},{"pid":"b9dece6d668756da1f090b03aab77e798a70f252","tid":1345791,"uid":28307,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T02:57:43.000Z","msg":"推  !<br />\n光復香港 ! 時代革命 !"},{"pid":"16e5c038b22ca6529931cac69b21391ef2cd422f","tid":1345791,"uid":28307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T03:00:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/yRhsGuf.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyRhsGuf.png&d=FZf2Eq7oNugCj0cVmX%2F%2Fqaix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=91a696fa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/yRhsGuf.png</a>"},{"pid":"cb15189ccf0bfaf8664dbdf95a7239f8fba16861","tid":1345791,"uid":251292,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T03:02:23.000Z","msg":"民意唔會逆轉架喇<br />\n成個月喇<br />\n明既就會明"},{"pid":"d4de30866b1411e50459d3ee210616fa6a10612e","tid":1345791,"uid":100847,"like":0,"dislike":0